          <div class="hero-btn" id="btn-rep-c"><svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#8b5cf6" stroke-width="2"><path d="m10.29 3.86L1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.42 0z"/></svg></div>
        </div>
        <div id="hero-quality"></div>
        <div id="hero-spinner"><div class="spin"></div></div>
        <div id="hero-err">
          <span style="font-size:32px;">📡</span>
          <p>No se pudo cargar la señal.</p>
          <button id="btn-retry">🔄 Reintentar</button>
        </div>
        <div id="hero-placeholder">
          <span style="font-size:40px;">📺</span>
          <p>Seleccioná un canal para comenzar</p>
        </div>
